<h1>fine art printing</h1>

<h3>a bespoke service for the creation of archival and giclee prints for artists</h3>

<p>dot-art offers a highly competitive and quality service for the creation of limited edition prints. 
Professional quality giclee prints can be prodcued on a choice of three 310gsm museum grade papers, using archival inks.
Our technician is available to advise on paper selection and file quality and answer any questions you may have.
Your prints can be ready for collection in Liverpool city centre within 48 hours of digital file receipt.</p>

<p>To place an order call 0845 017 6660 or 
<a href="mailto:printing@dot-art.co.uk">send us an email</a> quoting dot-art Printing Service.</p>

<h3>prices</h3>

<p>Bulk discounts and print storage also available, just ask.</p>

